New Records: England completed the second-highest successful ODI chase in the Caribbean Islands with 329 runs
Liam Livingstone scored his maiden ODI century
Key Match Events: England won the match by 5 wickets with 15 balls to spare
Post-Match Reflections: Liam Livingstone said, 'Certain things I have done in practice and at the end of the season in England felt like I have been getting back to my best. Maturing and I'm enjoying my cricket and if I'm enjoying my cricket, I play well. Pretty proud day.'
